      • addBrigade

        public void addBrigade(Pilot firstPilot,
              Pilot secondPilot,
              Navigator<java.lang.Object> navigator,
              Stewardess stewardess,
              Radioman radiomen,
              Flight flight)
        This method assigns a flight passed a group of employees consisting of two pilots and one staff (stewardess, navigator and radio operator) In the event that the method will not be transferred to at least one of the objects to be processed by an exception and the team will not be created and scheduled for flight
        Parameters:
        firstPilot - this object - first pilot in your new brigade
        secondPilot - this object - second pilot in your new brigade
        navigator - this object - navigator in your new brigade
        stewardess - this object - stewardess in your new brigade
        radiomen - this object - radioman in your new brigade
        flight - this object - brigade is going appointed on this flight
